e><blockquote><br />\n其實係咩病？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nanyway加油絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n腎病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好嚴重，會反覆個種？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反反覆覆 但又冇得斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如試下讀返書，再痛再算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知讀咩好 同埋讀書又要洗屋企人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵啲自己鍾意讀啦，搵工係有錢，但成世流流長，讀書之黎剩返既日子都係打工，同埋打工體力勞動多，始終讀書比較唔會捱壞你身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵啲鍾意讀嘅 讀完又搵唔到嘢做就pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過其實我係有諗過讀返書"},{"pid":"055788f5177d3ca85534898e303ba5c855dc2794","tid":243800,"uid":89732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1b8fce849ed06e41b52f2587c185fe3eb5a4711","tid":243800,"uid":89732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea13d3e25a595fdc2205745ec7a8f234ff82c179","tid":243800,"uid":9773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:02:28.000Z","msg":"讀門手藝囉一係<br />\n女仔讀美容，化妝，gel甲呢d 應該都搵到工生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84903bccae051b497772d3eabd691a0f7dce7a5","tid":243800,"uid":53370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n好嚴重，會反覆個種？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反反覆覆 但又冇得斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如試下讀返書，再痛再算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知讀咩好 同埋讀書又要洗屋企人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵啲自己鍾意讀啦，搵工係有錢，但成世流流長，讀書之黎剩返既日子都係打工，同埋打工體力勞動多，始終讀書比較唔會捱壞你身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵啲鍾意讀嘅 讀完又搵唔到嘢做就pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過其實我係有諗過讀返書</blockquote><br />\n唔好諗住後果先啦<br />\n人生苦短啊，諗太遠盞自己辛苦<br />\n不如讀自己想讀，出路再諗<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">餓唔死人嫁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老豆都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多謝你"},{"pid":"d846e721018814bd0edc7ea2813315537da93297","tid":243800,"uid":89732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4df05600f16b7d42fb4ce843f797385b86816366","tid":243800,"uid":89732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}